flowchart TD
    A[What do you need to test?] --> B{HUD display logic?}
    B -->|Yes| C{Needs animation?}
    C -->|No| D["Use animated: false\nAssert state immediately"]
    C -->|Yes| E["Use .animation(.none)\nor integration tests"]

    B -->|No| F{Business logic with HUD?}
    F -->|Yes| G["Create HUDDisplayable protocol\nUse MockHUDService in tests"]
    F -->|No| H{Custom indicator/progress?}
    H -->|Yes| I["Test start/stop state\nTest progress bounds\nTest intrinsicContentSize"]
    H -->|No| J{Delegate callbacks?}
    J -->|Yes| K["Conform test class to HUDDelegate\nAssert callback flags"]
    J -->|No| L["Use HUDStressTests patterns\nfor edge cases"]

    style D fill:#d4edda,stroke:#28a745
    style E fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#ffc107
    style G fill:#d4edda,stroke:#28a745
    style I fill:#d4edda,stroke:#28a745
    style K fill:#d4edda,stroke:#28a745
    style L fill:#cce5ff,stroke:#007bff
